<view class="page">
  <view class="material-head">
    <text class="eyebrow">材料</text>
    <view class="title">按用途补齐材料</view>
    <view class="muted copy">先补影响赔偿金额和文书生成的材料。每份材料都会说明为什么需要。</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="card state-card">正在加载材料清单...</view>
  <view wx:elif="{{error}}" class="danger-panel state-card">{{error}}</view>
  <view wx:elif="{{!materials.length}}" class="card empty-card">
    <view class="section-title">暂无材料清单</view>
    <view class="muted empty-copy">创建案件后，系统会按用途列出需要补充的材料。</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:else wx:for="{{materials}}" wx:key="group" class="group">
    <view class="section-title group-title">{{item.group}}</view>
    <view
      wx:for="{{item.items}}"
      wx:for-item="material"
      wx:key="name"
      class="card material-card"
    >
      <view class="material-info">
        <view class="material-name">{{material.name}}</view>
        <view class="muted purpose">{{material.purpose}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="material-side">
        <text class="pill {{material.status === '已通过' ? 'risk-low' : material.status === '需补充' ? 'risk-mid' : material.status === '无法识别' ? 'risk-high' : ''}}">
          {{material.status}}
        </text>
        <button class="upload-button" disabled="{{uploadingName === material.name}}" data-name="{{material.name}}" bindtap="upload">
          {{uploadingName === material.name ? '处理中' : material.status === '已通过' ? '查看' : material.status === '需补充' || material.status === '无法识别' ? '补充' : '上传'}}
        </button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="danger-panel">
    上传病历、身份证、收入证明等敏感材料前，正式版本会再次征得单独授权。高风险案件建议先人工复核。
  </view>
</view>
